imattas portfolio
==================

Personal portfolio for Ian Mattas / imattas, adapted from the Entropic Astro
textmode theme.

Commands
--------

    pnpm install --frozen-lockfile
    pnpm dev
    pnpm projects:import
    pnpm writeups:import
    pnpm check
    pnpm build

Main editing points:

    src/config/site.ts              home page text, links, and shared SEO metadata
    src/config/volumes.ts           volume titles and sorting
    src/content/philes/             portfolio notes
    src/layouts/base/BaseLayout.astro shared page-level SEO tags and JSON-LD
    src/modules/seo/                sitemap, RSS, excerpts, and structured-data helpers
    astro.config.mjs                canonical site URL

SEO
---

Base pages emit canonical URLs, crawl directives, author/keyword metadata,
Open Graph, Twitter Card tags, RSS discovery, theme metadata, and Schema.org
JSON-LD. Phile detail pages pass article titles, excerpts, authors, dates, and
page-specific keywords into the shared layout.

Writeups
--------

Volume 2 is imported from a local clone of:

    https://github.com/imattas/Writeups

The imported `.mdx` files are checked into the portfolio so GitHub Pages builds
normal static HTML without cloning another repo during deployment. To refresh
after cloning or updating the sibling repo at `../Writeups`:

    pnpm writeups:import

Projects
--------

Volume 1 is generated from public source repositories on:

    https://github.com/imattas

To refresh the checked-in project pages and README snapshots:

    pnpm projects:import

The original template is MIT licensed:

    https://github.com/CuB3y0nd/entropic
